data.description:
This amazing residence is situated in the heart of Desert Hills, nestled at the end of a paved cul-de-sac. The home boasts a spacious great room with an expansive breakfast bar and wet bar that seamlessly opens into a vast living area, complete with a formal dining space and a chef's kitchen. The kitchen features a generously sized island, luxurious granite countertops, and high-end finishes and detailing. Throughout the home, you'll find custom cabinetry and intricate woodworking, adding a touch of elegance to every corner.

This property offers three primary suites, each equipped with walk-in closets, along with an additional half bath and a den for added flexibility. The primary bathroom have undergone extensive renovation, providing a touch of modern luxury. For those with outdoor hobbies and interests, there are four horse stalls and a container tack shed to accommodate your equestrian needs. The property boasts two convenient pull-through RV gates, offering ample parking space for RVs, in addition to horse stalls.

The backyard is truly a resort-like oasis, complete with a large covered patio, a solar-heated pool, and Sliding doors with kid-safe latches make for convenient and secure access to the outdoors. Epoxy-coated garage floors come equipped with built-in cabinets and a stunning 336 square-foot studio. The property offers breathtaking panoramic mountain views, and the absence of an HOA, along with owned solar panels and city water, adds to its desirability. Whether you're looking to host gatherings or simply enjoy the finer things in life, this property is ready to meet your needs and more.
